metadata.name: PortalCards Special Edition : Alotta Feels #1/2
metadata.description: A open edition re-design, in honor of AlottaMoney, of the artist's experimental "Portalcards" NFTs created in 2020. Portalcards are collectible trading cards that feature notable Metaverse locations, along with relevant links, and a QR code that leads directly to the featured location when scanned.
